dct_title_s: International boundary between the State of Eritrea and the Federal Democratic Republic of Ethiopia
dct_description_sm: "This map was prepared in the Office of the Secretary of the Eritrea-Ethiopia Boundary Commision (EEBC), as an index to the series of 45 1:25,000 maps illustrating the statement issued by the EEBC on 27 November 2006 and has no independent standing of its own."
Inset: [Detail of the border near Tserona and Zalambessa].
Includes location map and list of boundary point coordinates.
